+publisher: "arXiv"
+url: "https://arxiv.org/html/2509.20353v2"
+author: "Viktoria Stray, Elias Goldmann Brandtzaeg, Viggo Tellefsen Wivestad, Astri Barbala, Nils Brede Moe"
